---
Source:
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
  ISBN: 978-1571746931
  Source:
    Title: The Gospel of Thomas
Page: 150
---
When you perceive that the two are One,
that the outer is the same as the inner,
that which is above is the same as that which is below,
that the male and the female are one and the same --
then you will enter the kingdom of God.
